OL,3,CEngland fans 'proud' of team despite
OL,4,Csemi-final loss
OL,6,FThere was disappointment for thousands
OL,7,Fof fans across the North West - who
OL,8,Fwatched England take on Argentina in a
OL,9,Fdramatic semi final of the World Cup.
OL,11,FAnthony Gordon's second-half opener
OL,12,Ffinally broke the deadlock after a
OL,13,Ftense and closely fought contest,
OL,14,Fputting England on course for their
OL,15,Ffirst men's World Cup final since Sir
OL,16,FAlf Ramsey's side lifted the trophy in
OL,17,F1966.
OL,19,FHundreds gathered at the Castlefield
OL,20,FBowl in Manchester to watch.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/4
