OL,3,CEngland fans 'proud' of team despite
OL,4,Csemi-final loss
OL,6,FBut the reigning champions refused to
OL,7,Fsurrender, and England began to lose
OL,8,Fcontrol of the match, with Jordan
OL,9,FPickford forced into a series of
OL,10,Fcrucial saves as the pressure mounted.
OL,12,FArgentina's breakthrough eventually
OL,13,Fcame in the final minutes, with two
OL,14,Flate goals by Enzo Fernandez and
OL,15,FLautaro Martinez - the second
OL,16,Fperfectly set up by Lionel Messi.
OL,18,FThe game ended 2-1.
OL,26,@vD@XrpwD@Mrt
