OL,3,CEngland fans 'proud' of team despite
OL,4,Csemi-final loss
OL,6,FAfter many England players left the
OL,7,Fpitch, gutted at their loss, captain
OL,8,FHarry Kane remained and clapped all of
OL,9,Fthe fans at the Atlanta stadium.
OL,11,F"I'm just gutted, gutted for the
OL,12,Fboys," he said in his post-match
OL,13,Finterview.
OL,15,F"I'm gutted for everyone, the team,
OL,16,Fthe staff, the fans. We played a good
OL,17,Fgame for the large majority of it.
OL,19,F"Once we went 1-0 up we seemed to just
OL,20,Ftry and hold on, which at this level
OL,21,Fis just not enough, so I'm gutted.
OL,26,@{D@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/4
