PN,36404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F364A1784207920
OL,3,CEngland fans 'proud' of team despite
OL,4,Csemi-final loss
OL,6,F"We worked so hard to be here. The
OL,7,Flads have given every last bit of
OL,8,Frunning, sweat, blood, tears, whatever
OL,9,Fit is, so to fall short like today is
OL,10,Fjust gutting."
OL,12,FArgentina are now set to face Spain on
OL,13,FSunday.
OL,15,FThe Three Lions will face France at
OL,16,F10pm BST on Saturday 18 July, in Miami
OL,17,F- in the third-place play-off.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@NO]
